## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

**How long does it take to integrate an AI chatbot with a CRM?**
If you are using a modern AI platform with native, no-code connectors (like Chatzy AI), you can often integrate with CRMs like HubSpot or Salesforce in under 10 minutes. Custom API integrations for legacy CRMs may take a few days of developer time.

**Can I connect my chatbot to a CRM without coding skills?**
Yes. Most leading AI chatbot platforms offer visual, drag-and-drop interfaces that allow you to authenticate your CRM account and map data fields without writing any code.

**What are the common challenges in chatbot-CRM synchronization?**
The most common challenges are poor data hygiene (syncing bad data into the CRM) and overly complex data mapping. It is highly recommended to start with a simple integration—like syncing name and email—before moving on to complex multi-step workflows.

**Does integrating a chatbot slow down the CRM?**
No. Chatbots communicate with CRMs via lightweight API calls, which are designed to handle massive amounts of data instantly without affecting system performance.

